<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire influence the distribution and patterning of this alliance. Uneven or scarce fires occur due to the location of stands in cooler drainage bottoms and cascades, adjacent to ephemeral streams, or near an occurrence of abundant bedrock and boulders (Potter 2005).</div>
